title: THE FALCON AND THE WINTER SOLDIER Episode 5 Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment:
Only 1 MORE EPISODE LEFT! What do you think will happen? #Zemodance?

For more Falcon videos check out my playlist: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7grJ0g-p4tZxGynJSnJ10OF
That was a rocky level montage for Sam

As a New Orleans native, it was an incredible surprise hearing The Meters legendary rendition of Hey Pocky A-Way during that Bucky/Falcon boat repair montage. Never thought I’d hear Mardi Gras music in the MCU. :)

Emotional episode. Loved the bro scenes between Falcon and the Winter Soldier, nearly cried when Isaiah shared his story, and Sam has an intense internal struggle about his future role. It was a great episode
Marvel is taking disarming to another level... Bucky actually has his arm removed. walker gets his arm broken and one chick even got a pole thrown straight through her shoulder.
description:
